stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Hidden: HUD initialized

    Hidden --> GraceWait: show(animated)
    Hidden --> Visible: show(animated: false)

    GraceWait --> Visible: graceTimer fired
    GraceWait --> Hidden: hide() before grace

    Visible --> AnimatingOut: hide(animated)
    Visible --> Hidden: hide(animated: false)
    Visible --> Visible: update progress/label/mode

    AnimatingOut --> Removed: animation complete
    Removed --> [*]: removeFromSuperview

    state Visible {
        [*] --> Displaying
        Displaying --> MinShowWait: hide() called, minShowTime active
        MinShowWait --> [*]: minShowTimer fired
    }

    note right of Removed: completionBlock called
    note right of GraceWait: Only if graceTime > 0
